{"tid":1330160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫香港人企最前既代價就係遠走他鄉，你仲諗住遊行完就算？","createTime":"2019-07-18T12:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T13:55:37.000Z","uid":89974,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"301e4001a7ef36f996b2fd62086426fb049cb16b","tid":1330160,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oz9REcC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOz9REcC.png&h=ac983998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190718&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59838175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190718%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59838175&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE2Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=2b5fff39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190718%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59838175&h=1953a2a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190718&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59838175</a><br />\n[url]http://【逆權運動】逾30名7.1衝擊立法會示威者抵台灣尋庇護[/url]<br />\n<br />\n前線手就污糟哂，又拆牆又血搏，幫全香港宣讀咗宣言，結果速龍一到就因為唔夠人要走，當日走到仲要擔心秋後算帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算和理非遊行如沙田上水屯門，一樣有手足拉咗番去比人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明71只要大家一齊守，人數愈多佢愈唔敢用過份暴力清場，有人比狗拉都可以救得番，就係因為我地淆底而棄前線不理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港仲有幾多人可以揮霍？今日前線死哂，聽日就到和理非企前線！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBe water 既結局就係棄卒保車，戇居個居！我尊重前線決定，但唔好係又叫散叫人be water ，每一次be water 我地都少緊手足！！！和理非比信心自己！比勇氣自己！每個人犧牲少少，就可以拯救到香港！<br />\n<br />\n留耐d 齊gear 721見！"},{"pid":"aff29f0f066bac7f08c1e9d2f7de0b2b761ea89f","tid":1330160,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a998c5ae49b19dccc2ce8df410b6b35c06e584a0","tid":1330160,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c58004375f81151831682d1f26ab062b55bdae","tid":1330160,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01374a7f624ab4e7c55fac72c6ce3001da9662a5","tid":1330160,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:41:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e8c4d9df142e43308b273f4d403b96e0f742ad1","tid":1330160,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70bb7fbec49375bec15d50354b751680767f35cb","tid":1330160,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:42:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"651c29088a907dfa9d3ed27a7395ac8b55985543","tid":1330160,"uid":274265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no